<br>
Find a repair man to give you an estimate to install a new door/frame/lock, whatever is needed in his &quot;expert&quot; opinion to correct the problem (not just changing the locks).  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> SEND THE FREAKING CERTIFIED LETTER WITH THIS ESTIMATE IN IT</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> detailing this will be done and deducted from rent in one week if the problem is not corrected.  Then deduct it from your rent when it is not done.<br>
<br>
